    <entry>
      <title>关于如何在VSCode环境基于STM32Cube插件使用DapLink进行调试的研究</title>
      <link href="/2026/04/28/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%A8VSCode%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ESTM32Cube%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8DapLink%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95%E7%9A%84%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6/"/>
      <url>/2026/04/28/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%A8VSCode%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8ESTM32Cube%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8DapLink%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95%E7%9A%84%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="关于如何在VSCode环境基于STM32Cube插件使用DapLink进行调试的研究"><a href="#关于如何在VSCode环境基于STM32Cube插件使用DapLink进行调试的研究" class="headerlink" title="关于如何在VSCode环境基于STM32Cube插件使用DapLink进行调试的研究"></a>关于如何在VSCode环境基于STM32Cube插件使用DapLink进行调试的研究</h2><h3 id="1-背景与动机"><a href="#1-背景与动机" class="headerlink" title="1. 背景与动机"></a>1. 背景与动机</h3><p>七月份电赛就要开打了，最近也是入手了两块天猛星的ti板子，想着先熟悉一下ti芯片的开发，顺手就购入了心心念念的DapLink（逻辑分析仪二合一）。本人虽然蛮久时间没有用过keil了，但是偶尔用上一次，令人心酸的代码补全和代码提示实在是让代码体验苦不堪言。于是跟着keysking的教程，我将整个开发工具链迁移到了我有较长使用经历的VSCode，并打算后续将包括嵌入式开发的整个环境迁移到Linux上去。总之就是这样，我虽然能够成功在VSCode使用STlink进行调试，但是ST插件没有对DapLink的支持，无法用我新买的DapLink进行调试实在是不够优雅，于是我踏上了对调试环境艰辛（也说不上）的探索。</p><h3 id="2-逻辑梳理"><a href="#2-逻辑梳理" class="headerlink" title="2. 逻辑梳理"></a>2. 逻辑梳理</h3><p>想要理解如何为什么要使用DapLink以及如何使用DapLink，就需要理清楚嵌入式开发和调试的整个逻辑链条。趁着这个机会，我也是完完整整地梳理了一遍开发流程，让我对嵌入式开发地理解更上了一层楼。</p><h4 id="核心组件与职责"><a href="#核心组件与职责" class="headerlink" title="核心组件与职责"></a>核心组件与职责</h4><ul><li>CMake：用于管理编译流程，指挥编译器生成elf文件，这个文件包含芯片的机器码和其他调试信息</li><li>ARM-GCC：编译器，用于连接源程序，生成可执行文件（对于芯片来说）</li><li>.elf文件：可执行文件，包含机器码、调试信息、符号表</li><li>OpenOCD：调试服务器，通过接受gdb请求并翻译成对应内存指令，传输到DapLink，驱动DapLink硬件进行芯片的读写操作</li><li>CMSIS-DAP 协议：OpenOCD支持的协议，由ARM公司官方制定的标准化协议，规定了调试软件和硬件的通信协议</li><li>GDB：调试客户端，通过接受用户在PC上的调试指令，像服务端发送请求，由OpenOCD创建的服务端会接受请求并下发到DapLink，进而完成内存读写操作</li><li>VSCode + STM32Cube插件：提供开发环境，提供面向用户的调试接口</li></ul><h3 id="3-环境搭建"><a href="#3-环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="3. 环境搭建"></a>3. 环境搭建</h3><ol><li>下载VSCode、STM32CubeMX等</li><li>在插件市场安装对应插件（<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1QfbpzGENy/">参考keysking教程(爽！手把手教你用VSCode开发STM32【大人，时代变啦！！！】</a>）</li><li>下载<a href="https://github.com/xpack-dev-tools/openocd-xpack/releases/">OpenOCD</a>，将可执行文件目录添加到Path，可在终端运行<code>openocd --version</code>判断是否安装正确</li><li>使用DAPLink连接目标芯片，运行<code>openocd -f interface/cmsis-dap.cfg -f target/stm32f1x.cfg</code>判断是否识别正确，配置文件参数须根据实际连接目标决定</li><li>配置VSCode launch.json，如果没有就自己在运行与调试（侧边栏）创建一个:</li></ol><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;configurations&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">[</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;type&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;stgdbtarget&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;request&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;launch&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;name&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;STM32Cube: Launch Generic GDB Server&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;origin&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;snippet&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;cwd&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;workspaceFolder&#125;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;preBuild&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;command:st-stm32-ide-debug-launch.build&#125;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;program&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;command:st-stm32-ide-debug-launch.get-projects-binary-from-context1&#125;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;gdb&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;command:st-stm32-ide-debug-launch.get-gdb-executable&#125;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;deviceName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;command:st-stm32-ide-debug-launch.get-device-name&#125;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;deviceCore&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;command:st-stm32-ide-debug-launch.get-core-name&#125;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;deviceTrustzone&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;TZ-disabled&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span>     <span class="comment">// 此处修改，按需求改为指定设备，不改应该也没问题</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;serverExe&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;openocd.exe&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span>           <span class="comment">// 此处修改，这里改成ocd文件名</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;serverParameters&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">[</span>                <span class="comment">// 此处修改</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-f&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span> <span class="string">&quot;interface/cmsis-dap.cfg&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span> <span class="comment">// 指定接口为 CMSIS-DAP (DAPLink)</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-f&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span> <span class="string">&quot;target/stm32f1x.cfg&quot;</span>     <span class="comment">// 指定目标设备，我这里是f103c8t6所以写得f1x，具体可以参考openocd目录里的配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="punctuation">]</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;serverHost&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;localhost&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span>          <span class="comment">// 这里修改，Openocd会把gdb服务器开在本地端口3333</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;serverPort&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;3333&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span>               <span class="comment">// 这里填端口</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;serverCwd&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;E:\\xpack-openocd-0.12.0-7\\bin&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span> <span class="comment">// 这里改成ocd目录</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;runEntry&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;main&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;imagesAndSymbols&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">[</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;imageFileName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;command:st-stm32-ide-debug-launch.get-projects-binary-from-context1&#125;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;imageOffset&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;symbolFileName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;command:st-stm32-ide-debug-launch.get-projects-binary-from-context1&#125;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;symbolOffset&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="punctuation">]</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-踩坑记录"><a href="#4-踩坑记录" class="headerlink" title="4.踩坑记录"></a>4.踩坑记录</h3><h4 id="一号小坑：GDB-server-is-undefined"><a href="#一号小坑：GDB-server-is-undefined" class="headerlink" title="一号小坑：GDB server is undefined"></a>一号小坑：GDB server is undefined</h4><p><em>现象：</em><br><code>bound doStepSettingsValidation Failed: GDB server is undefined, see serverExe &amp;&amp; serverCwd attributes</code><br><em>原因：</em> VSCode的STM32Cube插件找不到<code>openocd</code>命令，即使命令行中可以正常运行。此时并未配置ocd路径，只在server一栏中填入了<code>openocd</code><br><em>解决方案：</em> 同时指定路径和程序名字</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;serverExe&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;openocd.exe&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;serverCwd&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;E:\\xpack-openocd-0.12.0-7\\bin&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="二号小坑：deviceTrustzone-值不被接受"><a href="#二号小坑：deviceTrustzone-值不被接受" class="headerlink" title="二号小坑：deviceTrustzone 值不被接受"></a>二号小坑：deviceTrustzone 值不被接受</h4><p><em>现象：</em><br><code>值不被接受。有效值: &quot;Secure&quot;, &quot;Non-secure&quot;, &quot;Secure-only&quot;, &quot;TZ-disabled&quot;</code><br><em>原因：</em> deviceTrustzone 字段有严格的枚举值限制。<br><em>解决方案：</em> 感觉不是大问题，还没有试过没改会不会造成影响，反正TZ-disabled对应STM32设备，直接改成这个就行</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;deviceTrustzone&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;TZ-disabled&quot;</span>   <span class="comment">// 普通 STM32 芯片</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-一些FAQ"><a href="#6-一些FAQ" class="headerlink" title="6. 一些FAQ"></a>6. 一些FAQ</h3><h4 id="Q1：OpenOCD-支持哪些调试器？"><a href="#Q1：OpenOCD-支持哪些调试器？" class="headerlink" title="Q1：OpenOCD 支持哪些调试器？"></a>Q1：OpenOCD 支持哪些调试器？</h4><p>支持 CMSIS-DAP 协议的所有调试器，包括：</p><ul><li><p>DAPLink（各种国产开发板上的调试器）</p></li><li><p>Sipeed SLogic Combo 8（逻辑分析仪+DAPLink二合一）</p></li><li><p>正点原子、野火等开发板自带的 DAPLink</p></li></ul><h4 id="Q2：为什么-elf-文件不能直接烧录？"><a href="#Q2：为什么-elf-文件不能直接烧录？" class="headerlink" title="Q2：为什么 .elf 文件不能直接烧录？"></a>Q2：为什么 .elf 文件不能直接烧录？</h4><p>需要有软件（如 OpenOCD、ST-Link Utility）将 .elf 解析后，通过调试器（硬件）以 SWD&#x2F;JTAG 协议写入芯片 Flash。OpenOCD 扮演的就是这个“翻译官”角色。</p><h4 id="Q3：ST-Link-能用这个配置吗？"><a href="#Q3：ST-Link-能用这个配置吗？" class="headerlink" title="Q3：ST-Link 能用这个配置吗？"></a>Q3：ST-Link 能用这个配置吗？</h4><p>可以。将 serverParameters 中的接口文件改为：</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;-f&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span> <span class="string">&quot;interface/stlink.cfg&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="Q4：如何确认芯片型号对应的-target-配置文件？"><a href="#Q4：如何确认芯片型号对应的-target-配置文件？" class="headerlink" title="Q4：如何确认芯片型号对应的 target 配置文件？"></a>Q4：如何确认芯片型号对应的 target 配置文件？</h4><p>查看 OpenOCD 安装目录下的 scripts&#x2F;target&#x2F; 文件夹：</p><ul><li><p>STM32F103 系列 → stm32f1x.cfg</p></li><li><p>STM32F407 系列 → stm32f4x.cfg</p></li><li><p>STM32H743 系列 → stm32h7x.cfg</p></li></ul><h4 id="Q5：launch-json-中的-command-…-是什么？"><a href="#Q5：launch-json-中的-command-…-是什么？" class="headerlink" title="Q5：launch.json 中的 ${command:…} 是什么？"></a>Q5：launch.json 中的 ${command:…} 是什么？</h4><p>这是 VSCode 的命令变量，由插件动态计算。例如：</p><ul><li><p>get-gdb-executable：自动定位 arm-none-eabi-gdb 的路径</p></li><li><p>get-projects-binary-from-context1：自动获取项目编译生成的 .elf 文件路径</p></li></ul><h3 id="7-总结"><a href="#7-总结" class="headerlink" title="7. 总结"></a>7. 总结</h3><p>真是一场酣畅淋漓的调试，现在我可以通过DAPLink对任何芯片进行下载和调试了哈哈哈哈。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
